&lt;p&gt;· Strong customer service and interpersonal skills with the ability to build and maintain relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Proficient in using sales software, CRM systems, and MS Office Suite.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Strong organizational skills and attention to detail.&lt;/p&gt;
