&lt;p&gt;· Forklift operation certification (or willingness to obtain certification) is a plus.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Must be able to lift and carry items up to 50 pounds.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Ability to stand and walk for extended periods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation&lt;/strong&gt;: $28.97-35.40/hour, depending on experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
